 <li>under 16</li>\n  <li>16 to 19 and in full-time education (not higher than A-level or equivalent)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The parent who doesn&rsquo;t have day-to-day care of the child pays child maintenance to the parent or person who does. </p>\n\n<p>This person could be a grandparent or guardian as well as a parent. </p>\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"/arranging-child-maintenance-yourself\" title=\"arranging child maintenance yourself\">arrange child maintenance yourself</a> or the Child Support Agency (<abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr>) can sort it out for you - they&rsquo;ll work out how much should be paid, and they can also collect the payments for you.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can use the <a href=\"/calculate-child-maintenance\" title=\"child maintenance calculator\">child maintenance calculator</a> to get an idea of what payments might be.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Who can use the <abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr></h2>\n\n<p>You can apply to the <abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr> if you&rsquo;re:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the parent the child lives with</li>\n  <li>the parent the child doesn&rsquo;t live with</li>\n  <li>a grandparent or other guardian of the child</li>\n  <li>a child living in Scotland</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Who can&rsquo;t use the <abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr></h2>\n\n<p>You can&rsquo;t use the <abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr> if the receiving parent or the child lives outside the UK. </p>\n\n<p>If the paying parent lives abroad, the <abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr> can only help <a href=\"/child-maintenance-if-one-parent-lives-abroad\" title=\"child maintenance if one parent lives abroad\">in certain circumstances</a>. </p>\n\n<h2>What the <abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr> can help with</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Child Support Agency\">CSA</abbr> can help you:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>find the other parent if you don&rsquo;t know 